                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/11601.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Vera Cruz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-04-22T08:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 22, 1914, 8 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>American forces commenced advance to take entire city at eight o’clock under guns
                    of war vessels.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Canada</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
